docs/user/advanced.rst:295:.. _certifi: https://certifiio.readthedocs.io/
docs/user/advanced.rst-296-.. _Mozilla trust store: https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/raw-file/tip/security/nss/lib/ckfw/builtins/certdata.txt
